-ohm-plugin-misc
-PackageKit-qt
-qt-mobility
-telepathy-farsight
-telepathy-gabble
-telepathy-glib
-telepathy-mission-control
-telepathy-qt4
-telepathy-qt4-farsight
-telepathy-ring
